; Coverage for xact.cc lines 1029-1038 (check_exprs in auto_xact)
; Tests assert, check, and eval expressions in auto transactions.

= Expenses:Food
    assert amount > 0
    (Budget:Food)    -1

= Expenses:Rent
    check amount > 0
    (Budget:Rent)    -1

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Landlord
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Budget
24-Jan-01 Grocery               (Budget:Food)               $-10.00      $-10.00
24-Jan-02 Landlord              (Budget:Rent)              $-500.00     $-510.00
end test
